Toll Brothers - Wikipedia





















 






Toll Brothers

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Toll Brothers, Inc.





Type

Public


Traded as
NYSE: TOL
S&P 400 Component


Industry
Homebuilding


Founded
1967 (1967)


Founder
Robert I. Toll
Bruce E. Toll


Headquarters
Horsham, Pennsylvania, United States



Key people




Robert I. Toll (Chairman)
Douglas C. Yearley, Jr. (CEO)
Rick Hartman (President, COO)
Martin P. Connor (CFO)





Products
New homes and condos


Revenue



 US$3.91 billion (2014)
US$2.67 billion (2013)
US$1.88 billion (2012)






